Class OctaveFileWriter

    public class OctaveFileWriter
extends java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
    Octave text file format writer. Usage:
    1. call constructor
    2. call put for each variable to be stored.
    3. call writeFile(outputFilename) or setFilename(outputFilename) then writeFile()
    Author:
    Joseph Lizier (email, www)
